{"tid":1258154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環球時報》: 反對派勾結西方撼動不了香港大局","createTime":"2019-06-26T03:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T15:02:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":420,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"b01cd032d55e1d726e49cc28aaa012b588e33944","tid":1258154,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:11:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/06/10/2158536_f70f6b443d3b1bb97a838a207ac449cd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F2158536_f70f6b443d3b1bb97a838a207ac449cd.jpeg&h=73322359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(網上截圖)<br />\n<br />\n大量港人昨日上街抗議政府推行《逃犯條例》修訂，民陣稱有103萬人參加，規模超越2003年「7．1」50萬人上街反對23條立法。<br />\n<br />\n內地官媒《環球時報》發表題為「反對派勾結西方撼動不了香港大局」社評，批評主辦方故技重施「報大數」，「保公義撐修例大聯盟」同一天指已收到超過73萬名香港市民聯署支持修訂《逃犯條例》。<br />\n<br />\n社評指，這本是一項正常的特區立法活動，卻被反對派和國際上支持他們的力量進行了嚴重的政治化炒作，認為香港特區政府和主流民意為法治和公義而做的努力，絕不能半途而廢。<br />\n<br />\n社評續稱，國際上一些力量近一段時間與香港反對派明顯加強了互動，極力給這一修例行動貼上「威脅香港人權」的標簽，並分別在今年3月和5月訪問美國告洋狀，而美國眾議院議長佩洛西更接見到訪的香港反對派，這些都是香港激進反對派搞政治動員急需的彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n文章強調，香港事務純屬中國內政，香港反對派這種挾洋自重的政治操作方式既不得人心，也與落實「一國兩制」這一主題背道而馳。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2158536/%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82%3A%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%A0%B1%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8+%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E9%9B%A3%E9%98%BB%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2158536%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582%253A%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%2B%25E5%258B%25BE%25E7%25B5%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%2598%25BB%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=3ae8c8bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2158536/%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82%3A%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%A0%B1%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8+%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E9%9B%A3%E9%98%BB%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B</a>"},{"pid":"d73ca9ba8a16005f3dd919367f3dd952257f7db4","tid":1258154,"uid":88373,"like":788,"dislike":0,"score":788,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"即係有效"},{"pid":"e2eb4dc9b646595a04da20a758c7a0c576d43d62","tid":1258154,"uid":254594,"like":315,"dislike":1,"score":314,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"乖乖唔洗驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好快就唔再痛架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ffd38984bc422c0ef36b22862782c024f869f6","tid":1258154,"uid":169116,"like":200,"dislike":1,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:15:18.000Z","msg":"環時都驚驚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef1a981fd5f507023a6a6a2933acf40c2c37dab","tid":1258154,"uid":189356,"like":249,"dislike":0,"score":249,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:16:09.000Z","msg":"環你老母 球你老母   時你老母  報你老母<br />\n垃圾共狗飛機報 環咩球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682ac93e2136d66f042d67f3728655431969a404","tid":1258154,"uid":28279,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />闢謠即係真"},{"pid":"77f12060e58bc41479a8fd69e4069c3285e9d628","tid":1258154,"uid":159216,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"環時驚撚到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc73a3682f0575cda88af64a361d6507d3cc0f77","tid":1258154,"uid":64743,"li